import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['delay'].plot(kind='hist', bins=50, color='blue', edgecolor='black', alpha=0.7)
    plt.axvline(x=data['delay'].mean(), color='red', label='mean delay = {:.2f}'.format(data['delay'].mean()))
    plt.axvline(x=data['delay'].median(), color='green', label='median delay = {:.2f}'.format(data['delay'].median()))
    plt.legend()
    plt.title('What is the distribution of flight delays?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['distance'].plot(kind='box')
    plt.title('What is the average distance of flights?', wrap=True)
    plt.axvline(x=data['distance'].mean(), color='r', linestyle='--', label='Mean distance: {:.2f}'.format(data['distance'].mean()))
    plt.legend()
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['route'] = data['origin'] + ' to ' + data['destination']
    route_counts = data['route'].value_counts().sort_values(ascending=False)
    top_routes = route_counts.head(10)
    ax = top_routes.plot(kind='bar', color='blue')
    ax.set_xlabel('Route')
    ax.set_ylabel('Number of Flights')
    ax.axhline(y=top_routes.iloc[0], color='red', linestyle='--', label='Most Common Route: {:.2f}'.format(top_routes.iloc[0]))
    ax.legend()
    plt.title('What is the most common origin and destination for flights?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['date'], format='%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S', errors='coerce')
    fig, ax = plt.subplots()
    ax.scatter(data['distance'], data['delay'], alpha=0.5)
    ax.set_xlabel('Distance')
    ax.set_ylabel('Delay')
    plt.title('What is the relationship between distance and delay?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['date'], format='%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S', errors='coerce')
    data = data.sort_values(by='date')
    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(10, 6))
    ax.plot(data['date'], data.index, color='blue')
    ax.set_xlabel('Date')
    ax.set_ylabel('Number of Flights')
    ax.axvline(data['date'].min(), color='red', linestyle='--', label=f"First Flight: {data['date'].min().strftime('%Y-%m-%d')}")
    ax.axvline(data['date'].max(), color='green', linestyle='--', label=f"Last Flight: {data['date'].max().strftime('%Y-%m-%d')}")
    ax.legend()
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
